# Uniform-binding position: `attrs` referenced from inside an ordered-attrs
# `attrs={{ "k": v }}` literal pair value on a nested component tag. The pair
# Value field is `any`, so a plain string (from strAttr) is directly
# assignable — no assertion needed at the call site.
